<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_free">snd_compr_free</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/inode">inode</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/inode">inode</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/file">file</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">f</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_file">snd_compr_file</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">f</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/private_data">private_data</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_runtime">snd_compr_runtime</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">data</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/cancel_delayed_work_sync">cancel_delayed_work_sync</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/error_work">error_work</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/switch">switch</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">state</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_RUNNING">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_RUNNING</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_DRAINING">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_DRAINING</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_PAUSED">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_PAUSED</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">ops</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/trigger">trigger</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_TRIGGER_STOP">SNDRV_PCM_TRIGGER_STOP</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/break">break</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">default</span><span class="o">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/break">break</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">ops</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/free">free</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">!</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/dma_buffer_p">dma_buffer_p</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/kfree">kfree</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">buffer</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/kfree">kfree</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/kfree">kfree</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_update_tstamp">snd_compr_update_tstamp</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stream">snd_compr_stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_tstamp">snd_compr_tstamp</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/tstamp">tstamp</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">!</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">ops</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/pointer">pointer</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/ENOTSUPP">ENOTSUPP</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">ops</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/pointer">pointer</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/tstamp">tstamp</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/pr_debug">pr_debug</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&quot;dsp consumed till %d total %d bytes</span><span class="se">\n</span><span class="s">&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/tstamp">tstamp</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/byte_offset">byte_offset</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/tstamp">tstamp</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/copied_total">copied_total</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/direction">direction</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">==</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SND_COMPRESS_PLAYBACK">SND_COMPRESS_PLAYBACK</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/total_bytes_transferred">total_bytes_transferred</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/tstamp">tstamp</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/copied_total">copied_total</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">else</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/total_bytes_available">total_bytes_available</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/tstamp">tstamp</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/copied_total">copied_total</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/size_t">size_t</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_calc_avail">snd_compr_calc_avail</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stream">snd_compr_stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_avail">snd_compr_avail</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/memset">memset</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">sizeof</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="p">));</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_update_tstamp">snd_compr_update_tstamp</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/tstamp">tstamp</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="cm">/* Still need to return avail even if tstamp can&#39;t be filled in */</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/total_bytes_available">total_bytes_available</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">==</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">&amp;&amp;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">			</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">state</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">==</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_SETUP">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_SETUP</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">&amp;&amp;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">			</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/direction">direction</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">==</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SND_COMPRESS_PLAYBACK">SND_COMPRESS_PLAYBACK</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/pr_debug">pr_debug</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&quot;detected init and someone forgot to do a write</span><span class="se">\n</span><span class="s">&quot;</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/buffer_size">buffer_size</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/pr_debug">pr_debug</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&quot;app wrote %lld, DSP consumed %lld</span><span class="se">\n</span><span class="s">&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">			</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/total_bytes_available">total_bytes_available</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">			</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/total_bytes_transferred">total_bytes_transferred</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/total_bytes_available">total_bytes_available</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">==</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">				</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/total_bytes_transferred">total_bytes_transferred</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/direction">direction</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">==</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SND_COMPRESS_PLAYBACK">SND_COMPRESS_PLAYBACK</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">			</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/pr_debug">pr_debug</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&quot;both pointers are same, returning full avail</span><span class="se">\n</span><span class="s">&quot;</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">			</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/buffer_size">buffer_size</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">else</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">			</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/pr_debug">pr_debug</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&quot;both pointers are same, returning no avail</span><span class="se">\n</span><span class="s">&quot;</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">			</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/total_bytes_available">total_bytes_available</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">			</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/total_bytes_transferred">total_bytes_transferred</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/direction">direction</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">==</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SND_COMPRESS_PLAYBACK">SND_COMPRESS_PLAYBACK</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/buffer_size">buffer_size</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/pr_debug">pr_debug</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&quot;ret avail as %lld</span><span class="se">\n</span><span class="s">&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kr">inline</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/size_t">size_t</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_get_avail">snd_compr_get_avail</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stream">snd_compr_stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_avail">snd_compr_avail</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_calc_avail">snd_compr_calc_avail</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_ioctl_avail">snd_compr_ioctl_avail</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stream">snd_compr_stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">unsigned</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">long</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">arg</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_avail">snd_compr_avail</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">ioctl_avail</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/size_t">size_t</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_calc_avail">snd_compr_calc_avail</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">ioctl_avail</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n">ioctl_avail</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/switch">switch</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">state</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_OPEN">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_OPEN</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EBADFD">EBADFD</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_XRUN">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_XRUN</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EPIPE">EPIPE</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">default</span><span class="o">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/break">break</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/copy_to_user">copy_to_user</a></span><span class="p">((</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/__u64">__u64</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/__user">__user</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">arg</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">				</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">ioctl_avail</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">sizeof</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">ioctl_avail</span><span class="p">)))</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EFAULT">EFAULT</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_write_data">snd_compr_write_data</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stream">snd_compr_stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	       </span><span class="k">const</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">char</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/__user">__user</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">buf</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/size_t">size_t</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">count</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="kt">void</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/dstn">dstn</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/size_t">size_t</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/copy">copy</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_runtime">snd_compr_runtime</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="cm">/* 64-bit Modulus */</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/u64">u64</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/app_pointer">app_pointer</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/div64_u64">div64_u64</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/total_bytes_available">total_bytes_available</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">				    </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/buffer_size">buffer_size</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/app_pointer">app_pointer</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/total_bytes_available">total_bytes_available</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		      </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/app_pointer">app_pointer</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/buffer_size">buffer_size</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/dstn">dstn</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">buffer</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">+</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/app_pointer">app_pointer</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/pr_debug">pr_debug</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&quot;copying %ld at %lld</span><span class="se">\n</span><span class="s">&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">			</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">unsigned</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">long</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">count</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/app_pointer">app_pointer</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">count</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/buffer_size">buffer_size</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/app_pointer">app_pointer</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/copy_from_user">copy_from_user</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/dstn">dstn</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">buf</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">count</span><span class="p">))</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">			</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EFAULT">EFAULT</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">else</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/copy">copy</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/buffer_size">buffer_size</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/app_pointer">app_pointer</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/copy_from_user">copy_from_user</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/dstn">dstn</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">buf</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/copy">copy</a></span><span class="p">))</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">			</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EFAULT">EFAULT</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/copy_from_user">copy_from_user</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">buffer</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">buf</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">+</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/copy">copy</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">count</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/copy">copy</a></span><span class="p">))</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">			</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EFAULT">EFAULT</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="cm">/* if DSP cares, let it know data has been written */</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">ops</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/ack">ack</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">ops</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/ack">ack</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">count</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">count</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/ssize_t">ssize_t</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_write">snd_compr_write</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/file">file</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">f</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">const</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">char</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/__user">__user</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">buf</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/size_t">size_t</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">count</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/loff_t">loff_t</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">offset</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_file">snd_compr_file</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">f</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/private_data">private_data</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stream">snd_compr_stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/size_t">size_t</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_BUG_ON">snd_BUG_ON</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">!</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="p">))</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EFAULT">EFAULT</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/mutex_lock">mutex_lock</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/device">device</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">lock</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="cm">/* write is allowed when stream is running or has been steup */</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/switch">switch</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">state</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_SETUP">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_SETUP</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_PREPARED">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_PREPARED</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_RUNNING">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_RUNNING</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/break">break</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">default</span><span class="o">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/mutex_unlock">mutex_unlock</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/device">device</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">lock</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EBADFD">EBADFD</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_get_avail">snd_compr_get_avail</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/pr_debug">pr_debug</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&quot;avail returned %ld</span><span class="se">\n</span><span class="s">&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">unsigned</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">long</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="cm">/* calculate how much we can write to buffer */</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">count</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">count</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">ops</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/copy">copy</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="kt">char</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/__user">__user</a></span><span class="o">*</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/cbuf">cbuf</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">char</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/__user">__user</a></span><span class="o">*</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">buf</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">ops</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/copy">copy</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/cbuf">cbuf</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">else</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_write_data">snd_compr_write_data</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">buf</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/total_bytes_available">total_bytes_available</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">+=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="cm">/* while initiating the stream, write should be called before START</span>
<span class="cm">	 * call, so in setup move state */</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">state</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">==</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_SETUP">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_SETUP</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">state</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_PREPARED">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_PREPARED</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/pr_debug">pr_debug</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&quot;stream prepared, Houston we are good to go</span><span class="se">\n</span><span class="s">&quot;</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/mutex_unlock">mutex_unlock</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/device">device</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">lock</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>


<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/ssize_t">ssize_t</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_read">snd_compr_read</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/file">file</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">f</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">char</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/__user">__user</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">buf</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/size_t">size_t</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">count</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/loff_t">loff_t</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">offset</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_file">snd_compr_file</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">f</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/private_data">private_data</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stream">snd_compr_stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/size_t">size_t</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_BUG_ON">snd_BUG_ON</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">!</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="p">))</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EFAULT">EFAULT</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/mutex_lock">mutex_lock</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/device">device</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">lock</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="cm">/* read is allowed when stream is running, paused, draining and setup</span>
<span class="cm">	 * (yes setup is state which we transition to after stop, so if user</span>
<span class="cm">	 * wants to read data after stop we allow that)</span>
<span class="cm">	 */</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/switch">switch</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">state</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_OPEN">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_OPEN</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_PREPARED">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_PREPARED</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_SUSPENDED">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_SUSPENDED</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_DISCONNECTED">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_DISCONNECTED</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EBADFD">EBADFD</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">goto</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">out</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_XRUN">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_XRUN</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EPIPE">EPIPE</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">goto</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">out</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_get_avail">snd_compr_get_avail</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/pr_debug">pr_debug</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&quot;avail returned %ld</span><span class="se">\n</span><span class="s">&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">unsigned</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">long</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="cm">/* calculate how much we can read from buffer */</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">count</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">count</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">ops</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/copy">copy</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">ops</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/copy">copy</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">buf</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">else</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/ENXIO">ENXIO</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">goto</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">out</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/total_bytes_transferred">total_bytes_transferred</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">+=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="nl">out</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/mutex_unlock">mutex_unlock</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/device">device</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">lock</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_mmap">snd_compr_mmap</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/file">file</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">f</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/vm_area_struct">vm_area_struct</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/vma">vma</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/ENXIO">ENXIO</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/__poll_t">__poll_t</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_get_poll">snd_compr_get_poll</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stream">snd_compr_stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/direction">direction</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">==</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SND_COMPRESS_PLAYBACK">SND_COMPRESS_PLAYBACK</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EPOLLOUT">EPOLLOUT</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">|</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EPOLLWRNORM">EPOLLWRNORM</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">else</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EPOLLIN">EPOLLIN</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">|</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EPOLLRDNORM">EPOLLRDNORM</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/__poll_t">__poll_t</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_poll">snd_compr_poll</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/file">file</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">f</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/poll_table">poll_table</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/wait">wait</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_file">snd_compr_file</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">f</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/private_data">private_data</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stream">snd_compr_stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/size_t">size_t</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/__poll_t">__poll_t</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_BUG_ON">snd_BUG_ON</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">!</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="p">))</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EPOLLERR">EPOLLERR</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/mutex_lock">mutex_lock</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/device">device</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">lock</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/switch">switch</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">state</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_OPEN">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_OPEN</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_XRUN">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_XRUN</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_get_poll">snd_compr_get_poll</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">|</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EPOLLERR">EPOLLERR</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">goto</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">out</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">default</span><span class="o">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/break">break</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/poll_wait">poll_wait</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">f</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/sleep">sleep</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/wait">wait</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_get_avail">snd_compr_get_avail</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/pr_debug">pr_debug</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&quot;avail is %ld</span><span class="se">\n</span><span class="s">&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">unsigned</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">long</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="cm">/* check if we have at least one fragment to fill */</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/switch">switch</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">state</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_DRAINING">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_DRAINING</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="cm">/* stream has been woken up after drain is complete</span>
<span class="cm">		 * draining done so set stream state to stopped</span>
<span class="cm">		 */</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_get_poll">snd_compr_get_poll</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">state</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_SETUP">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_SETUP</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/break">break</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/avail">avail</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">&gt;=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/fragment_size">fragment_size</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">			</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_get_poll">snd_compr_get_poll</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/break">break</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">default</span><span class="o">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_get_poll">snd_compr_get_poll</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">|</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EPOLLERR">EPOLLERR</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/break">break</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="nl">out</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/mutex_unlock">mutex_unlock</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/device">device</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">lock</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_get_caps">snd_compr_get_caps</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stream">snd_compr_stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">unsigned</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">long</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">arg</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/memset">memset</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/caps">caps</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">sizeof</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/caps">caps</a></span><span class="p">));</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/copy_to_user">copy_to_user</a></span><span class="p">((</span><span class="kt">void</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/__user">__user</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">arg</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/caps">caps</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">sizeof</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/caps">caps</a></span><span class="p">)))</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="cp">#ifndef <a href="v6.0/C/ident/COMPR_CODEC_CAPS_OVERFLOW">COMPR_CODEC_CAPS_OVERFLOW</a></span>

<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/ENOMEM">ENOMEM</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">goto</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">out</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/copy_to_user">copy_to_user</a></span><span class="p">((</span><span class="kt">void</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/__user">__user</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">arg</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/caps">caps</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">sizeof</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/caps">caps</a></span><span class="p">)))</span><span class="w"></span>
