<span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_malloc_pages">snd_compr_malloc_pages</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stream">snd_compr_stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/size_t">size_t</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">size</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_dma_buffer">snd_dma_buffer</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/dmab">dmab</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">ret</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_BUG_ON">snd_BUG_ON</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">!</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">||</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">!</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="p">))</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EINVAL">EINVAL</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/dmab">dmab</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/kzalloc">kzalloc</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">sizeof</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/dmab">dmab</a></span><span class="p">),</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/GFP_KERNEL">GFP_KERNEL</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">!</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/dmab">dmab</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/ENOMEM">ENOMEM</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/dmab">dmab</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">dev</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/dma_buffer">dma_buffer</a></span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">dev</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n">ret</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_dma_alloc_pages">snd_dma_alloc_pages</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/dmab">dmab</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">dev</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">type</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/dmab">dmab</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">dev</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">dev</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">size</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/dmab">dmab</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">ret</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/kfree">kfree</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/dmab">dmab</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="cm">/* revisit this with snd_pcm_preallocate_xxx */</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_allocate_buffer">snd_compr_allocate_buffer</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stream">snd_compr_stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_params">snd_compr_params</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/params">params</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="kt">void</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">buffer</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nb">NULL</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/buffer_size">buffer_size</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/params">params</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">buffer</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/fragment_size">fragment_size</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/params">params</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">buffer</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/fragments">fragments</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">ops</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/copy">copy</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n">buffer</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nb">NULL</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="cm">/* if copy is defined the driver will be required to copy</span>
<span class="cm">		 * the data from core</span>
<span class="cm">		 */</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">else</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/dma_buffer_p">dma_buffer_p</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">			</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/buffer_size">buffer_size</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/dma_buffer_p">dma_buffer_p</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/bytes">bytes</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">				</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/dev_err">dev_err</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/device">device</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">dev</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">						</span><span class="s">&quot;Not enough DMA buffer&quot;</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">			</span><span class="k">else</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">				</span><span class="n">buffer</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/dma_buffer_p">dma_buffer_p</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/area">area</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">		</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">else</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">			</span><span class="n">buffer</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/kmalloc">kmalloc</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/buffer_size">buffer_size</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/GFP_KERNEL">GFP_KERNEL</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">!</span><span class="n">buffer</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">			</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/ENOMEM">ENOMEM</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/fragment_size">fragment_size</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/params">params</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">buffer</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/fragment_size">fragment_size</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/fragments">fragments</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/params">params</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">buffer</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/fragments">fragments</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">buffer</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">buffer</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/buffer_size">buffer_size</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/buffer_size">buffer_size</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compress_check_input">snd_compress_check_input</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_params">snd_compr_params</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/params">params</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="cm">/* first let&#39;s check the buffer parameter&#39;s */</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/params">params</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">buffer</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/fragment_size">fragment_size</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">==</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">||</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	    </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/params">params</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">buffer</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/fragments">fragments</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/U32_MAX">U32_MAX</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">/</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/params">params</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">buffer</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/fragment_size">fragment_size</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">||</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	    </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/params">params</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">buffer</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/fragments">fragments</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">==</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EINVAL">EINVAL</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="cm">/* now codec parameters */</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/params">params</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">codec</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">id</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">==</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">||</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/params">params</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">codec</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">id</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SND_AUDIOCODEC_MAX">SND_AUDIOCODEC_MAX</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EINVAL">EINVAL</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/params">params</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">codec</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/ch_in">ch_in</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">==</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">||</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/params">params</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">codec</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/ch_out">ch_out</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">==</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EINVAL">EINVAL</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_set_params">snd_compr_set_params</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stream">snd_compr_stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">unsigned</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">long</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">arg</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_params">snd_compr_params</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/params">params</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">state</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">==</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_OPEN">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_OPEN</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="cm">/*</span>
<span class="cm">		 * we should allow parameter change only when stream has been</span>
<span class="cm">		 * opened not in other cases</span>
<span class="cm">		 */</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/params">params</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/memdup_user">memdup_user</a></span><span class="p">((</span><span class="kt">void</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/__user">__user</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">arg</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">sizeof</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/params">params</a></span><span class="p">));</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/IS_ERR">IS_ERR</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/params">params</a></span><span class="p">))</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">			</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/PTR_ERR">PTR_ERR</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/params">params</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">		</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compress_check_input">snd_compress_check_input</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/params">params</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">			</span><span class="k">goto</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">out</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">		</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_allocate_buffer">snd_compr_allocate_buffer</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/params">params</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">			</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/ENOMEM">ENOMEM</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">			</span><span class="k">goto</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">out</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">		</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">ops</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/set_params">set_params</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/params">params</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">			</span><span class="k">goto</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">out</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/metadata_set">metadata_set</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/false">false</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/next_track">next_track</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/false">false</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">state</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_SETUP">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_SETUP</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">else</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EPERM">EPERM</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="nl">out</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/kfree">kfree</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/params">params</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_get_params">snd_compr_get_params</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stream">snd_compr_stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">unsigned</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">long</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">arg</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_codec">snd_codec</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/params">params</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">!</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">ops</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/get_params">get_params</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EBADFD">EBADFD</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/params">params</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/kzalloc">kzalloc</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">sizeof</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/params">params</a></span><span class="p">),</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/GFP_KERNEL">GFP_KERNEL</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">!</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/params">params</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/ENOMEM">ENOMEM</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">ops</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/get_params">get_params</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/params">params</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">goto</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">out</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/copy_to_user">copy_to_user</a></span><span class="p">((</span><span class="kt">char</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/__user">__user</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">arg</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/params">params</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">sizeof</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/params">params</a></span><span class="p">)))</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EFAULT">EFAULT</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="nl">out</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/kfree">kfree</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/params">params</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_get_metadata">snd_compr_get_metadata</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stream">snd_compr_stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">unsigned</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">long</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">arg</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_metadata">snd_compr_metadata</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/metadata">metadata</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">!</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">ops</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/get_metadata">get_metadata</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/ENXIO">ENXIO</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/copy_from_user">copy_from_user</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/metadata">metadata</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">void</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/__user">__user</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">arg</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">sizeof</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/metadata">metadata</a></span><span class="p">)))</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EFAULT">EFAULT</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">ops</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/get_metadata">get_metadata</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/metadata">metadata</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">!=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/copy_to_user">copy_to_user</a></span><span class="p">((</span><span class="kt">void</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/__user">__user</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">arg</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/metadata">metadata</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">sizeof</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/metadata">metadata</a></span><span class="p">)))</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EFAULT">EFAULT</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_set_metadata">snd_compr_set_metadata</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stream">snd_compr_stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">unsigned</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">long</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">arg</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_metadata">snd_compr_metadata</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/metadata">metadata</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">!</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">ops</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/set_metadata">set_metadata</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/ENXIO">ENXIO</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="cm">/*</span>
<span class="cm">	* we should allow parameter change only when stream has been</span>
<span class="cm">	* opened not in other cases</span>
<span class="cm">	*/</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/copy_from_user">copy_from_user</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/metadata">metadata</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">void</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/__user">__user</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">arg</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">sizeof</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/metadata">metadata</a></span><span class="p">)))</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EFAULT">EFAULT</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">ops</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/set_metadata">set_metadata</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/metadata">metadata</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/metadata_set">metadata_set</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/true">true</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kr">inline</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_tstamp">snd_compr_tstamp</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stream">snd_compr_stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">unsigned</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">long</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">arg</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_tstamp">snd_compr_tstamp</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/tstamp">tstamp</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">};</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">ret</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n">ret</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_update_tstamp">snd_compr_update_tstamp</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/tstamp">tstamp</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">ret</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">==</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n">ret</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/copy_to_user">copy_to_user</a></span><span class="p">((</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_tstamp">snd_compr_tstamp</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/__user">__user</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">arg</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">			</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/tstamp">tstamp</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">sizeof</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/tstamp">tstamp</a></span><span class="p">))</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">?</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EFAULT">EFAULT</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">ret</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_pause">snd_compr_pause</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stream">snd_compr_stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/switch">switch</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">state</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_RUNNING">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_RUNNING</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">ops</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/trigger">trigger</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_TRIGGER_PAUSE_PUSH">SNDRV_PCM_TRIGGER_PAUSE_PUSH</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">!</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">			</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">state</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_PAUSED">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_PAUSED</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/break">break</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_DRAINING">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_DRAINING</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">!</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/device">device</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/use_pause_in_draining">use_pause_in_draining</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">		</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">ops</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/trigger">trigger</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_TRIGGER_PAUSE_PUSH">SNDRV_PCM_TRIGGER_PAUSE_PUSH</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">!</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">			</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/pause_in_draining">pause_in_draining</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/true">true</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">default</span><span class="o">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EPERM">EPERM</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_resume">snd_compr_resume</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stream">snd_compr_stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/switch">switch</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">state</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">!</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">			</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">state</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_RUNNING">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_RUNNING</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">!</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/pause_in_draining">pause_in_draining</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">		</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">ops</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/trigger">trigger</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_TRIGGER_PAUSE_RELEASE">SNDRV_PCM_TRIGGER_PAUSE_RELEASE</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">			</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/pause_in_draining">pause_in_draining</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/false">false</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
