<span class="w">	</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_start">snd_compr_start</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stream">snd_compr_stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/switch">switch</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">state</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_SETUP">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_SETUP</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/direction">direction</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">!=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SND_COMPRESS_CAPTURE">SND_COMPRESS_CAPTURE</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">			</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EPERM">EPERM</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/break">break</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_PREPARED">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_PREPARED</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/break">break</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">default</span><span class="o">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EPERM">EPERM</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">ops</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/trigger">trigger</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_TRIGGER_START">SNDRV_PCM_TRIGGER_START</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">!</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">state</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_RUNNING">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_RUNNING</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stop">snd_compr_stop</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stream">snd_compr_stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/switch">switch</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">state</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_OPEN">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_OPEN</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_SETUP">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_SETUP</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_PREPARED">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_PREPARED</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EPERM">EPERM</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">default</span><span class="o">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/break">break</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">ops</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/trigger">trigger</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_TRIGGER_STOP">SNDRV_PCM_TRIGGER_STOP</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">!</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="cm">/* clear flags and stop any drain wait */</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/partial_drain">partial_drain</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/false">false</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/metadata_set">metadata_set</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/false">false</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/pause_in_draining">pause_in_draining</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/false">false</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_drain_notify">snd_compr_drain_notify</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/total_bytes_available">total_bytes_available</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/total_bytes_transferred">total_bytes_transferred</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">void</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/error_delayed_work">error_delayed_work</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/work_struct">work_struct</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/work">work</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stream">snd_compr_stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/container_of">container_of</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/work">work</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stream">snd_compr_stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/error_work">error_work</a></span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/work">work</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/mutex_lock">mutex_lock</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/device">device</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">lock</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">ops</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/trigger">trigger</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_TRIGGER_STOP">SNDRV_PCM_TRIGGER_STOP</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/wake_up">wake_up</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/sleep">sleep</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/mutex_unlock">mutex_unlock</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/device">device</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">lock</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="cm">/**</span>
<span class="cm"> * snd_compr_stop_error: Report a fatal error on a stream</span>
<span class="cm"> * @stream: pointer to stream</span>
<span class="cm"> * @state: state to transition the stream to</span>
<span class="cm"> *</span>
<span class="cm"> * Stop the stream and set its state.</span>
<span class="cm"> *</span>
<span class="cm"> * Should be called with compressed device lock held.</span>
<span class="cm"> *</span>
<span class="cm"> * Return: zero if successful, or a negative error code</span>
<span class="cm"> */</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stop_error">snd_compr_stop_error</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stream">snd_compr_stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">			 </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_pcm_state_t">snd_pcm_state_t</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">state</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">state</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">==</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">state</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">state</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">state</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/pr_debug">pr_debug</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&quot;Changing state to: %d</span><span class="se">\n</span><span class="s">&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">state</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/queue_delayed_work">queue_delayed_work</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/system_power_efficient_wq">system_power_efficient_wq</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/error_work">error_work</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EXPORT_SYMBOL_GPL">EXPORT_SYMBOL_GPL</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stop_error">snd_compr_stop_error</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compress_wait_for_drain">snd_compress_wait_for_drain</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stream">snd_compr_stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">ret</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="cm">/*</span>
<span class="cm">	 * We are called with lock held. So drop the lock while we wait for</span>
<span class="cm">	 * drain complete notification from the driver</span>
<span class="cm">	 *</span>
<span class="cm">	 * It is expected that driver will notify the drain completion and then</span>
<span class="cm">	 * stream will be moved to SETUP state, even if draining resulted in an</span>
<span class="cm">	 * error. We can trigger next track after this.</span>
<span class="cm">	 */</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">state</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_DRAINING">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_DRAINING</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/mutex_unlock">mutex_unlock</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/device">device</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">lock</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="cm">/* we wait for drain to complete here, drain can return when</span>
<span class="cm">	 * interruption occurred, wait returned error or success.</span>
<span class="cm">	 * For the first two cases we don&#39;t do anything different here and</span>
<span class="cm">	 * return after waking up</span>
<span class="cm">	 */</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n">ret</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/wait_event_interruptible">wait_event_interruptible</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/sleep">sleep</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">			</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">state</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">!=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_DRAINING">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_DRAINING</a></span><span class="p">));</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">ret</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">==</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/ERESTARTSYS">ERESTARTSYS</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/pr_debug">pr_debug</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&quot;wait aborted by a signal</span><span class="se">\n</span><span class="s">&quot;</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">else</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">ret</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/pr_debug">pr_debug</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&quot;wait for drain failed with %d</span><span class="se">\n</span><span class="s">&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">ret</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>


<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/wake_up">wake_up</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/sleep">sleep</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/mutex_lock">mutex_lock</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/device">device</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">lock</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">ret</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_drain">snd_compr_drain</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stream">snd_compr_stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/switch">switch</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">state</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_OPEN">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_OPEN</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_SETUP">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_SETUP</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_PREPARED">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_PREPARED</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_PAUSED">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_PAUSED</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EPERM">EPERM</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_XRUN">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_XRUN</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EPIPE">EPIPE</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">default</span><span class="o">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/break">break</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">ops</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/trigger">trigger</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SND_COMPR_TRIGGER_DRAIN">SND_COMPR_TRIGGER_DRAIN</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/pr_debug">pr_debug</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&quot;SND_COMPR_TRIGGER_DRAIN failed %d</span><span class="se">\n</span><span class="s">&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/wake_up">wake_up</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/sleep">sleep</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compress_wait_for_drain">snd_compress_wait_for_drain</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_next_track">snd_compr_next_track</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stream">snd_compr_stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="cm">/* only a running stream can transition to next track */</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">state</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">!=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_RUNNING">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_RUNNING</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EPERM">EPERM</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="cm">/* next track doesn&#39;t have any meaning for capture streams */</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/direction">direction</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">==</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SND_COMPRESS_CAPTURE">SND_COMPRESS_CAPTURE</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EPERM">EPERM</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="cm">/* you can signal next track if this is intended to be a gapless stream</span>
<span class="cm">	 * and current track metadata is set</span>
<span class="cm">	 */</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/metadata_set">metadata_set</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">==</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/false">false</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EPERM">EPERM</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">ops</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/trigger">trigger</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SND_COMPR_TRIGGER_NEXT_TRACK">SND_COMPR_TRIGGER_NEXT_TRACK</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">!=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/metadata_set">metadata_set</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/false">false</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/next_track">next_track</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/true">true</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_partial_drain">snd_compr_partial_drain</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stream">snd_compr_stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/switch">switch</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">state</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_OPEN">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_OPEN</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_SETUP">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_SETUP</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_PREPARED">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_PREPARED</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_PAUSED">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_PAUSED</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EPERM">EPERM</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">case</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nl"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_PCM_STATE_XRUN">SNDRV_PCM_STATE_XRUN</a></span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EPIPE">EPIPE</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">default</span><span class="o">:</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/break">break</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="cm">/* partial drain doesn&#39;t have any meaning for capture streams */</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/direction">direction</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">==</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SND_COMPRESS_CAPTURE">SND_COMPRESS_CAPTURE</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EPERM">EPERM</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="cm">/* stream can be drained only when next track has been signalled */</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/next_track">next_track</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">==</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/false">false</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EPERM">EPERM</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/partial_drain">partial_drain</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/true">true</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">ops</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/trigger">trigger</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SND_COMPR_TRIGGER_PARTIAL_DRAIN">SND_COMPR_TRIGGER_PARTIAL_DRAIN</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/pr_debug">pr_debug</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&quot;Partial drain returned failure</span><span class="se">\n</span><span class="s">&quot;</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/wake_up">wake_up</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/runtime">runtime</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/sleep">sleep</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/next_track">next_track</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/false">false</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compress_wait_for_drain">snd_compress_wait_for_drain</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">long</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_ioctl">snd_compr_ioctl</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/file">file</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">f</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">unsigned</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">cmd</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">unsigned</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">long</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">arg</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_file">snd_compr_file</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">f</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/private_data">private_data</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr_stream">snd_compr_stream</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/stream">stream</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">retval</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/ENOTTY">ENOTTY</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/compr">compr</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/device">device</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/device_data">device_data</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">			</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/compr">compr</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/direction">direction</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/compr">compr</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/proc_root">proc_root</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nb">NULL</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kr">inline</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">void</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compress_set_id">snd_compress_set_id</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr">snd_compr</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/compr">compr</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">const</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">char</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">id</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/strscpy">strscpy</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/compr">compr</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">id</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">id</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">sizeof</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/compr">compr</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">id</span><span class="p">));</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="cp">#else</span>
<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kr">inline</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compress_proc_init">snd_compress_proc_init</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr">snd_compr</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/compr">compr</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kr">inline</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">void</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compress_proc_done">snd_compress_proc_done</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr">snd_compr</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/compr">compr</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kr">inline</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">void</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compress_set_id">snd_compress_set_id</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr">snd_compr</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/compr">compr</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">const</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">char</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">id</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="cp">#endif</span>

<span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compress_dev_free">snd_compress_dev_free</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_device">snd_device</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/device">device</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr">snd_compr</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/compr">compr</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/compr">compr</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/device">device</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/device_data">device_data</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compress_proc_done">snd_compress_proc_done</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/compr">compr</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/put_device">put_device</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/compr">compr</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">dev</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="cm">/**</span>
<span class="cm"> * snd_compress_new: create new compress device</span>
<span class="cm"> * @card: sound card pointer</span>
<span class="cm"> * @device: device number</span>
<span class="cm"> * @dirn: device direction, should be of type enum snd_compr_direction</span>
<span class="cm"> * @id: ID string</span>
<span class="cm"> * @compr: compress device pointer</span>
<span class="cm"> *</span>
<span class="cm"> * Return: zero if successful, or a negative error code</span>
<span class="cm"> */</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compress_new">snd_compress_new</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_card">snd_card</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">card</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/device">device</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">			</span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/dirn">dirn</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">const</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">char</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">id</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compr">snd_compr</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/compr">compr</a></span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">const</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">struct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_device_ops">snd_device_ops</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">ops</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/dev_free">dev_free</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compress_dev_free">snd_compress_dev_free</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/dev_register">dev_register</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compress_dev_register">snd_compress_dev_register</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/dev_disconnect">dev_disconnect</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compress_dev_disconnect">snd_compress_dev_disconnect</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="p">};</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">ret</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/compr">compr</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">card</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">card</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/compr">compr</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/device">device</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/device">device</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/compr">compr</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/direction">direction</a></span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/dirn">dirn</a></span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/mutex_init">mutex_init</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/compr">compr</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">lock</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compress_set_id">snd_compress_set_id</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/compr">compr</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">id</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_device_initialize">snd_device_initialize</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/compr">compr</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">dev</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">card</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/dev_set_name">dev_set_name</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/compr">compr</a></span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n">dev</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s">&quot;comprC%iD%i&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">card</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/number">number</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/device">device</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="n">ret</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_device_new">snd_device_new</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">card</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/SNDRV_DEV_COMPRESS">SNDRV_DEV_COMPRESS</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/compr">compr</a></span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">ops</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">ret</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">==</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="w">		</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compress_proc_init">snd_compress_proc_init</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/compr">compr</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="w">	</span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">ret</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="p">}</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/EXPORT_SYMBOL_GPL">EXPORT_SYMBOL_GPL</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/snd_compress_new">snd_compress_new</a></span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>

<span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/MODULE_DESCRIPTION">MODULE_DESCRIPTION</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&quot;ALSA Compressed offload framework&quot;</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/MODULE_AUTHOR">MODULE_AUTHOR</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&quot;Vinod Koul &lt;vinod.koul@linux.intel.com&gt;&quot;</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
<span class="n"><a href="v6.0/C/ident/MODULE_LICENSE">MODULE_LICENSE</a></span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&quot;GPL v2&quot;</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"></span>
